---

<section class="tiles">
  <div class="tile tile-violet">
    <span class="caption">ROHKAFFEE ANGEBOT</span>
    <h3>Der Kaffee<br />der bleibt</h3>
    <p class="tile-text">
      Die Zukunft des Kaffees beginnt mit neuen Arten. Excelsa ist eine seltene,
      klimaresiliente Kaffeeart mit neuen Geschmacksprofilen und Zukunft für den
      Kaffeeanbau.
    </p>
    <a href="/kaffee" class="btn btn-secondary">
      <span>Unserer Kaffee</span>
      <svg class="arrow" width="14" height="11" viewBox="0 0 14 11" fill="none">
        <path d="M1 5.5h12m0 0L8.5 1M13 5.5L8.5 10" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="tile tile-green">
    <span class="caption">ORIGINS</span>
    <h3>Gemeinsam<br />in die Zukunft</h3>
    <p class="tile-text">
      Durch faire Partnerschaften, klimaresiliente Anbausysteme und bessere
      Marktchancen stärken wir die Zukunft des Kaffeeanbaus.
    </p>
    <a href="/origins" class="btn btn-secondary">
      <span>Unsere Origins</span>
      <svg class="arrow" width="14" height="11" viewBox="0 0 14 11" fill="none">
        <path d="M1 5.5h12m0 0L8.5 1M13 5.5L8.5 10" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tiles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--warm-dark-grey);
  }

  .tile {
    padding: 40px 60px 60px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 16px;
    min-height: 428px;
    border: none;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .tile + .tile {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--warm-dark-grey);
  }

  .tile-violet {
    background: var(--violet);
  }

  .tile-green {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #f5f5f5;
  }

  .caption {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--type-caption);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: 1.96px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .tile-violet .caption {
    color: var(--warm-dark-grey);
  }

  .tile-green .caption {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--type-heading-sm);
    line-height: 0.92;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .tile-text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--type-copy-fluid);
    line-height: 1.3;
    max-width: 547px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--warm-dark-grey);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-control);
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--type-button);
    margin-top: 16px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    filter: brightness(1.15);
    transform: scale(1.01);
  }

  .arrow {
    width: 14px;
    height: 11px;
    transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(0) !important;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover .arrow {
    transform: rotate(0deg) translateX(4px) !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tiles {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .tile {
      padding: 32px 24px 40px;
      min-height: 320px;
    }

    .tile + .tile {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--warm-dark-grey);
      border-left: none;
    }
  }
</style>
